{"tid":910352,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"世界之最列表","createTime":"2018-11-21T06:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T06:32:48.000Z","uid":21424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"65516e8629d48b15a686141857dd861162b6f6dd","tid":910352,"uid":21424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:20:06.000Z","msg":"人口密度最高的地區 - 旺角<br />\n平均密度為每平方公里13萬人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n奪得最多獎項及連續次數的藝人 - <img src=\"https://evchk.fandom.com/wiki/%E5%AE%B9%E7%A5%96%E5%85%92?file=ZAf1tDJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%2585%2592%3Ffile%3DZAf1tDJ.jpg&h=a17dba11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由2000年起到現在合共奪得近千個獎項成為全球最大贏家，其中她連續十四次奪得「最優秀流行女歌手」大獎的最高記錄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B9%8B%E6%9C%80%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=3epJlx%2FWQLZ2qb6f%2B2woDDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=68eb69f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B9%8B%E6%9C%80%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a>"},{"pid":"c2c2768a13ae31a8e6e5b5ad5da2cef4e1508e60","tid":910352,"uid":21424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"全球最長工時（瑞銀報告2015）<br />\n全球最高樓價（世邦報告2015年10月）<br />\n樓價與家庭收入比率全球最高（2015）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face